data.description: One owner home in Stone Horse built in 2020. 4/2/3 with island in kitchen, granite, gas range, microwave, walk-in pantry. Split floorplan, double sink in Master. Covered patio & porch. Neighborhood pool & playground. Patio plumbed for gas grill.
